數位系統設計 Design of Digital System

大學部一年級必修課程。
近五年開課情形：1012、1022、1031、1041、1051、1061(預定開課)。
105學年度第一學期課程大綱。
Textbook 
      
“Digital design”, M. Mano and M. Ciletti, Pearson Prentice Hall 2013 
          (5th Edition)


Topics include 
      
Digital system and binary numbers
          
Class note: Ch1-part1 (1.2-1.4) written version.
Class note: Ch1-part2 (1.5) written version.
Class note: Ch1-part3 (1.6) written version.
Class note: Ch1-part4 (1.7-1.9) written version.


Boolean algebra and logic gates
		  
Class note: Ch2-part1 (2.1-2.3) written version.
Class note: Ch2-part2 (2.4) written version.
Class note: Ch2-part3 (2.5) written version.
Class note: Ch2-part4 (2.6) written version.
Class note: Ch2-part5 (2.7-2.8) written version.


Gate-level minimization
		  
Class note: Ch3-part1 (3.1-3.3).
Class note: Ch3-part2 (3.4).
Class note: Ch3-part3 (3.5).
Class note: Ch3-part4 (3.6).
Class note: Ch3-part5 (3.7).
Class note: Ch3-part6 (3.8).


Combinational logic
          
Class note: Ch4-part1 (4.1-4.3).
Class note: Ch4-part2 (4.5).
Class note: Ch4-part3 (4.6).
Class note: Ch4-part4 (4.7).
Class note: Ch4-part5 (4.8).
Class note: Ch4-part6 (4.9-4.10).
Class note: Ch4-part7 (4.11).


Synchronous sequential logic
          
Class note: Ch5-part1 (5.1-5.2).
Class note: Ch5-part2 (5.3).
Class note: Ch5-part3 (5.4).
Class note: Ch5-part4 (5.5).
Class note: Ch5-part5 (5.7).
Class note: Ch5-part6 (5.8). Updated on 12/14.


Registers and counters
          
Class note: Ch6-part1 (6.1-6.2).
Class note: Ch6-part2 (6.3).
Class note: Ch6-part3 (6.4-6.5).


Memory and programmable logic (ppt)


Grading

Homework and Quiz 40%
Midterm 30%
Final 30%


